
    

    Before Docker
    1. write application code 
    2. install neccessary dependencies 
    3. test it locally
    4. prepare deployememt artifacts(also known as builds). 
    5. install all the dependencies with same version on sevrers that you want to deploy to your app.


    After Docker
    1. write application code
    2. Build dockerfile & Image
    3. Deploy the docker container on server.


What is Docker ?
Docker is Containerization platform for packaging, deploying, and running applications as Containers.
